query:
UPDATE user_health_profiles
                    SET max_heart_rate = $1,
                        hr_zone_1_max = $2,
                        hr_zone_2_max = $3,
                        hr_zone_3_max = $4,
                        hr_zone_4_max = $5,
                        hr_zone_5_max = $6,
                        vt0_threshold = $7,
                        vt1_threshold = $8,
                        vt2_threshold = $9
                    WHERE user_id = $10
